			],
			"description": "This folder contains authentication endpoints required to access DSV’s secured APIs.\n\nUse these endpoints to:\n\n- Obtain a new `access_token` using client credentials\n    \n- Refresh the token using a valid `refresh_token`\n    \n\nThe retrieved `access_token` must be included in the `Authorization` header (`Bearer`) for all subsequent API requests.\n\nA Postman test script is included to automatically extract and store the `access_token` and `refresh_token` as **collection variables**, so they can be reused across the collection without manual copying."
		},
